Title: WOMENS LONG CARDIGAN
Body (HTML): According to this week's forecast, it's safe to pack away winter's beloved parka. Luckily, in it's place is a lightweight knit cardigan that's perfect for throwing on over your favorite jeans and button down or if it's warmer where you are (we Angelenos are basking in 75 degree temps during this "winter" week), a pair of shorts and a tee.
